snippet.title: ★v4.8 [The Phantom of the Theater] Trailer★- Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
S-rank battlesuit [Starchasm Nyx] is debuting in the upcoming v4.8 [The Phantom of the Theater]!
v4.8 also features the new event [Stan Wars] as well as the new weapon [Sanguine Gaze] and stigma set [Verne (T, M, B)]! Don't miss them!

Subscribe our YouTube and turn on notification for latest video : http://bit.ly/HonkaiImpact3rdYTB
